There were several issues though:
- we said we‚Äôd check in at 8pm, but we actually came to town at around 5. They let us leave the bags but the apartment was not cleaned and we were informed about it. If you ask me - if the check in is at 3pm, the apartment should be ready regardless of the guests coming later;
- there‚Äôs only one set of keys for an apartment for 4+ people, this was extremely inconvenient. When I asked for another set I was offered to pay for it. This is weird, a deposit I would understand but why would I pay for the keys that I leave behind in 4 days. Please consider offering 2 sets of keys to the guests who come in companies;
- the ventilation didn‚Äôt switch off at all and we were told a specialist would come and check it - no one came; it was noisy 24/7
